<D>__{too much. they do that to you, too, you know.}
<A>__{they seek to destroy every facet of ali's life. ali knows that. as they pass the pumps. some customers recognize him.}
<C>__{chauncey eskridge }
<D>__{where you goin'?}
<C>__{ali}
<P>__{(to customers)}
<D>__{look out!}
<C>__{customer}
<D>__{hey, champ!}
<A>__{and ali pretends to start sparring. the working men laugh. one is brave enough to raise his hands, too. ali smiles and trades a couple of phantom slaps. it breaks off. he made their day. he shakes each of their hands. his spirit's raised, he walks off. chauncey watches this ritual...}
